snippet.title: Eternal Skirmish Tornado Escape
snippet.description:
Knight eamon gets rooted and cannot move. In addition to that, wizard Fisk summons a geyser under him and magician Fia summon meteor that will burn him. Fortunately, druid Corann can summon tornado that will rescue him!

Play Eternal Skirmish now! https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.funhappens.eternalskirmish
Checkout our Facebook https://www.facebook.com/eternalskirmish/
Talk with us on Reddit https://www.reddit.com/r/EternalSkirmish/
Find more info on our Wiki http://eternal-skirmish.wikia.com/wiki/Eternal_Skirmish_Wiki
